64
00:04:55,434 --> 00:05:01,375
A parent nucleus, P, decays into a daughter
nucleus D via emission of a He-4 nucleus.

65
00:05:01,375 --> 00:05:07,575
This corresponds to a spontaneous fission
into daughter nuclei of vary asymmetric mass,

66
00:05:07,575 --> 00:05:11,189
