84
00:06:32,780 --> 00:06:38,330
The parent nucleus can of course also
directly decay to the ground state

85
00:06:38,330 --> 00:06:41,340
without passing by intermediate states.

86
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:46,145
This direct decay results in
the most energetic alpha particle.

87
