relativistic but still impressive.

104
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:12,100
It has a velocity of about
0.15 speed of light.

105
00:08:13,380 --> 00:08:18,490
Confined to a region with a radius of
about 10^-12 centimeters,

106
00:08:18,490 --> 00:08:23,522
the particle bounces off the barrier
with a frequency of about

107
00:08:23,522 --> 00:08:28,822
4.5 10^21 times per second.

108
00:08:28,822 --> 00:08:37,240
The probability of penetration per second is thus
0.5 10^-18 per second.

109
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:42,577
